{"tid":438525,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港成亞洲生活最貴城市 主因樓價高企","createTime":"2017-10-17T04:00:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-17T05:04:40.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0ce97ba7a5b5cdb236406f700b1d93797c67d3cd","tid":438525,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T04:00:27.000Z","msg":"瑞士寶盛私人銀行（Julius Bar)發表財富報告，指香港取代上海成為亞洲生活最昂貴的城市，主要是指數比重最大是房地產，因此推高了指數。<br />\n<br />\n報告指，香港豪宅每平方米為51594美元(約40.24萬港元)，較亞洲平均價格水平19150美元高出2.69倍，瑞士寶盛私人銀行亞洲投資總監 Bhaskar Laxminarayan 指出，由於房地產佔指數30%，若樓價保持平穩，香港排名仍然會高企。<br />\n<br />\n同時香港為高級餐飲試味套餐及商務艙機票價格最貴城市。吉隆坡則是最便宜的城市，主要得益於當地貨幣下跌。<br />\n<br />\n以平均加權計算，上海連續三年成為最昂貴項目數量最多的城市，主要由於去年人民幣貶值。<br />\n<br />\n記者：龍彩霞<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1508212302828&amp;issue=20171017\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1508212302828%26issue%3D20171017&d=YGZ%2BIxeYTalUZFmtas2VCDANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=0ac8a4a6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1508212302828%26issue%3D20171017&h=15634eaa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1508212302828&amp;issue=20171017</a>"},{"pid":"2f389696e721bd26f0abd638428f6d56795071a7","tid":438525,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T04:01:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.finews.asia/images/cache/c7e97834ccf260869a7ccab577bb2614_w500.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.finews.asia%2Fimages%2Fcache%2Fc7e97834ccf260869a7ccab577bb2614_w500.jpg&h=4917f455&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"20681fa31a3ea99933649b0ad8d4c162836bb0f6","tid":438525,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T05:04:40.000Z","msg":"Oct 17近期活躍五毛<br />\n1三色貓<br />\n2群龍共舞<br />\n3法國佬巫斯義=香港鍵國<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">4真律師何君堯</span><br />\n5newlif